# JobAgent runs entirely from local config (backend/data/app_settings.json +
# backend/data/profile.json). No environment variables are required to run in
# mock mode.
#
# Optional: your Anthropic API key for real job search + Claude-drafted replies.
# You normally set this in the app's Settings page (stored locally in
# app_settings.json, never committed). If you prefer an env var for development:
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
#
# Gmail (live inbox) is configured via the Settings page by pointing at your
# Google OAuth client-secret file — see the README. Nothing goes here.
